### Create action using curl
POST http://localhost:3000/api/actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "format": "curl",
  "content": "curl http://localhost:3000/api/dummy",
  "actionName": "accountUpgrade",
  "description": "upgrade the account"
}

### Create action using OpenAPI spec (YAML)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/actions/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "openapi",
  "content": "openapi: 3.0.3\ninfo:\n  title: Dummy API\n  version: 1.0.0\n  description: A simple API for account upgrade operations\nservers:\n  - url: http://localhost:3000\n    description: Local development server\npaths:\n  /api/dummy:\n    get:\n      operationId: accountUpgrade\n      summary: Upgrade the account\n      description: Initiates an account upgrade process\n      responses:\n        '200':\n          description: Successful response\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                type: object\n                properties:\n                  status:\n                    type: string\n                    example: success\n                  message:\n                    type: string\n                    example: Account upgraded successfully"
}

